skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie trivia
des: Movie trivia is a simple trivia game in Q&A format. Every question has multiple choices and the user is prompted to choose one. Choose the option that you think is correct and Alexa will tell you if it is. No additional account setup is needed for this skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
